{"article_id":"C89YfkgnZlt6x9Ag","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Aiming to bolster his case for a wall along the U.S. border with Mexico ,","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"President Donald Trump said on Monday","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"he would make a prime-time televised address","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"and visit the border this week","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"as the government marked its 17th day of a partial shutdown .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"who now control the U.S. House of Representatives ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"have rejected Trump ' s demand for $ 5.7 billion","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"to help build a wall .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Without a deal on that sticking point ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"talks","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"to fund the government","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"have stalled .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence said","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Trump had not made a decision about his threat","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"to declare a national emergency","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"and build a wall","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"without congressional approval .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"Asked about the possibility of legal challenges and whether the White House counsel ' s office had reviewed the matter thoroughly ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Pence told reporters :","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"\" They ' re looking at it ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"and the president is considering it . \"","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"Trump ' s speech ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"planned for 9 p.m. on Tuesday","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"( 0200 GMT Wednesday )","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"and the border trip on Thursday","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"underscored his resolve","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"not to back off his 2016 campaign promise","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"to build a wall","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"he believes","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"will stem illegal immigration and drug trafficking .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"He promised during the campaign","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"that Mexico would pay for the wall .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Mexico has refused to do so .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"All the major U.S. television networks agreed to air Trump ' s speech .","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"Democrats in Congress ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"who say","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"a wall would be expensive , inefficient and immoral ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"called for the networks to grant them equal time in a joint statement","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"issued by House Speaker Nancy Pelosi and Senate Democratic leader Chuck Schumer .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"\" Now that the television networks have decided to air the President ' s address ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"which","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"if his past statements are any indication","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"will be full of malice and misinformation ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"Democrats must immediately be given equal airtime , \"","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"the statement said .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Pressure","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"to reach a deal","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"to end the shutdown","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"is likely to grow","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"as its effects are increasingly felt ,","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"including possible cuts in food stamp programs for the poor .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"The acting director of the White House ' s Office of Management and Budget , Russ Vought , said","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"tax refunds would be distributed","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"despite the shutdown .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"White House spokeswoman Sarah Sanders announced the border trip on Twitter","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"without providing details .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"The visit will likely highlight security concerns","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"pushed by the administration as justification for the wall .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"\" The president ' s position is :","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"There is a crisis at the southern border ,","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"and Democrats are refusing to negotiate , \"","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Pence said .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump speaks to the media","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"as he returns from Camp David to the White House in Washington , U.S. , January 6 , 2019 .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"/Joshua Roberts","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"The emphasis on a \" crisis \" could be the administration ' s attempt","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"to lay the groundwork for a potential emergency declaration .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Such a decision would almost certainly face a legal challenge .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Trump has tried to link terrorism to illegal immigration ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"without providing evidence ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"as justification for the plan .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Democrats say","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"there has been no evidence of suspected terrorists coming through the southern border","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"and that Trump has no grounds","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"to declare a national emergency over the issue .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"Large chunks of the federal government shut down on Dec. 22 over Trump ' s demand","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"that a bill","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"to keep the federal government operational","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"include more than $ 5 billion","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"to pay for what he has now said","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"would be a steel structure","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"to protect the border .","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"About 800,000 government workers are furloughed or working without pay .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Pence said","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"Trump also invited Democrats back to the White House","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"to respond to its latest proposal","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"to resolve the standoff over legislation","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"to fund the government .","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"The vice president ,","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"who participated in weekend discussions on the shutdown ,","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"Democratic staff said","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"there would be no negotiations","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"until the government is reopened .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"Trump said in December","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"he would be \" proud \" to shut the government down over the wall","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"and told lawmakers last week","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"it could last months .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"The president skipped a planned trip to Florida","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"to stay in Washington","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"during the Christmas and New Year ' s holidays","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"after the partial shutdown began .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"He exhorted Democrats in Congress to \" come back from vacation \"","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"and approve funding for his wall .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"Democrats returned to Washington in the new year ,","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"taking control of the House ,","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"and passed legislation","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"to reopen all closed government agencies","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"but did not include wall funding .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"This week , they will pass a series of bills","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"to reopen federal agencies .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"Secretary of Homeland Security Kirstjen Nielsen told reporters in a briefing on Monday","depth":4},{"id":115,"text":"that terrorists had crossed the border into the United States","depth":5},{"id":116,"text":"but that information about the number of such incidents was sensitive or classified .","depth":5},{"id":117,"text":"Democrats say","depth":4},{"id":118,"text":"other border security measures are more efficient and cost-effective than a wall ,","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"which","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"they say","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"is contrary to American values .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":243,"left":0,"right":242,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":242,"left":234,"right":241,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":168,"right":233,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":156,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":143,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":126,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":123,"right":124,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":142,"left":133,"right":141,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":133,"left":129,"right":132,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"left":127,"right":128,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":127,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":10,"right":131,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":131,"left":130,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":130,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":137,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":14,"right":136,"relation":"attributio